<figureCitation id="A6E785B05F72CA5774BAD1C291C646BB" captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F7787300" captionText="Figure 5. Distribution map for Pareuryaptus spp. known from China: P. adoxus (Tschitscherine) (blue); P. exiguus Dubault, Lassalle &amp; Roux (red); P. luangphabangensis Kirschenhofer (orange); P. chalceolus chalceolus (Bates) (green); P. chalceolus formosanus (Jedlicka) (magenta)." figureDoi="10.3897/BDJ.10.e84104.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/677579" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104">5</figureCitation>
.
</paragraph>
